
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Hardie Web Services - Under Construction</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Adam Hardie, the developer behind Hardie Web Services, is crafting something new." />
    <style>
      :root {
        --background-color: #0f172a; /* Dark background */
        --primary-color: #fbbf24;    /* Accent color (e.g., Amber-400) */
        --text-color: #ffffff;      /* White text */
        --font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        background: var(--background-color);
        color: var(--text-color);
        font-family: var(--font-family);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0 1rem;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        width: 90%;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: var(--primary-color);
      }

      .cta {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
        color: var(--primary-color);
        background: transparent;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
      }

      .cta:hover {
        background: var(--primary-color);
        color: var(--background-color);
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 120px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <h1>
        Hardie <span class="highlight">Web Services</span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        Howdy, I'm Adam, the developer behind <span class="highlight">Hardie Web Services</span>.
        We're passionate about crafting modern, accessible websites 
        and digital experiences that help businesses thrive.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our site is currently undergoing some exciting changes. 
        Check back soon for fresh designs, insights on web development, 
        and the latest projects I'm working on.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:adam.hardie13@gmail.com" class="cta">
        Contact Me
      </a>

      <footer>
        2025 <span class="highlight">Hardie Web Services</span> &copy; - All rights reserved
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
